Package: bodsr
Type: Package
Title: An R wrapper for pulling data from the Bus Open Data Service ('BODS') API (<https://www.bus-data.dft.gov.uk/>) 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Francesca", "Bryden", , "francesca.bryden@dft.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This allows users to download 'BODS' transport information from the API.
    This includes timetable and fare metadata (including links for full datasets) and real-time location data in both xml or GTFS-RT formats.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Imports: httr, jsonlite, xml2, dplyr, purrr, tibble, rlang
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
